Step#01:
install node.js
Step#02:
open terminal in vs code and write:
    npm init -y
    npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite
    npx tailwindcss init -postcss

Step#03:
create a css file "input.css",write this:

    @tailwind base;
    @tailwind components;
    @tailwind utilities;

add this file into your html file.

Step#04:
in tailwind.config.js file replace: 
    content[], with content["*"]

Step#05:
    add "start" : "vite" in scripts in your package.json

Step#06:
then run this command:
    npm run start 
